original_title: Brooklyn: Neptune Avenue - Van Sicklen Place
text:
(1)
542-544 Neptune Ave., at the S.E. corner of Van Sicklen Place, showing the Conrad House.
December 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2)
The same, looking south. Also shown is the Culver Line of the B.M.T.
1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(3)
The same, looking east; this presents a rear view of the houses.
December 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
